1. Ethical Considerations
Potential Biases & Mitigation Strategies:

Model	Potential Biases	Mitigation Tools
MNIST Classifier	- Cultural bias in digit writing styles
- Age bias (elderly/child handwriting)
- Accessibility bias (amputee writing)	TensorFlow Fairness Indicators
1. Analyze performance by demographic subgroups
2. Apply adversarial debiasing during training
3. Implement min-diff loss for fairness constraints
Amazon Reviews NER	- Brand name recognition favors Western companies
- Product bias against local/artisanal items
- Sentiment lexicon cultural differences	spaCy Rule-based Systems
1. Add custom patterns for underrepresented brands
2. Create culture-specific sentiment rules
3. Implement context-aware entity
